// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2358 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 87be0274-2cc6-56c5-a873-fc2b861475c1

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
